      "body" : "This looks reasonable to me, utACK.  This will fix the issues that `test/functional/combine_logs` has with tests using mocktime, right?\r\n\r\n@laanwj I'd personally prefer to have the extra timestamp on each line when using mocktime -- one use case I have is for my simulation environment, where mocktime is set on every message (tx, block, etc) that is delivered to bitcoind.  Adding an extra line for each change in mocktime would add substantial clutter, and also make reading/parsing the actual debug output more difficult (the mocktime is usually more interesting to me than the system time).  ",
